    "description": "<ul><li><p><span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">Your Pact Weapon gains an additional 1 point Weapon Property. You can change the chosen Weapon Property when you complete a Quick Rest.</span></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> You need to add that Property manually</em></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">You learn 1 Attack Maneuver.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">You can spend MP on Martial Enhancements and Maneuver performed with your Pact Weapon. When you do, you gain </span><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"1\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\"><strong>2 SP</strong></span><span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"2\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\"> worth of Enhancements per MP spent.</span></p></li></ul>",
